---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  const posts = [
    {
      slug: "why-72-21-7-is-best",
      title: "The Science of Comfort: Why 72/21/7 is the Gold Standard",
      date: "April 10, 2026",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A0064eeab34cc43ffaad5a0739e62beafC.png",
      keywords: "72% Polyester 21% Rayon 7% Spandex, medical scrub fabric, healthcare uniform material",
      description: "A deep dive into the textile engineering behind the most successful medical scrub brands.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">For decades, the medical apparel industry was dominated by heavy, stiff cotton. But as shifts became longer and the physical demands on healthcare workers increased, the need for a 'performance gear' approach became evident. At Yilong Scrubs, our research led us to the <strong>72/21/7 Signature Blend.</strong></p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A0064eeab34cc43ffaad5a0739e62beafC.png" alt="Close-up of premium scrub fabric texture" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl border-8 border-slate-50" />

        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mt-20 mb-8 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Solving the "Stiffness" Pain Point</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">The most common complaint from medical professionals is uniforms that restrict movement. Traditional scrubs often felt like cardboard after a few washes. Our 72/21/7 blend addresses this by providing a multi-functional matrix:</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 my-16">
          <div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 font-black italic">72%</div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-xl mb-4 italic">Polyester: The Backbone</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Polyester provides the structural integrity and durability needed for 50+ industrial washes without fading or pilling. It is the core of our wrinkle-resistance technology.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 text-secondary flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 font-black italic">21%</div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-xl mb-4 italic">Rayon: The Soul</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">A semi-synthetic fiber that mimics the feel of silk. It provides the ultra-soft hand-feel and moisture-wicking properties essential for staying fresh through double shifts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 font-black italic">7%</div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-xl mb-4 italic">Spandex: The Engine</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Delivers the critical 4-way stretch. Whether you're performing CPR or assisting a patient, this fabric moves with you, never against you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="border-l-8 border-primary p-10 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-r-[3rem] italic my-16 text-2xl leading-relaxed">
          "When we developed our 205GSM Elite series, we weren't just making clothes. We were engineering a toolkit for the modern healer." — Yilong Textile Lab
        </blockquote>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Overcoming the Transparency Issue</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Cheap scrubs are often thin and see-through, a major pain point for nurses. By precisely controlling the GSM (Grams per Square Meter) and the weave density of our 72/21/7 blend, Yilong ensures 100% opacity across all colors, from Deep Navy to Sage Green.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "future-of-ai-in-manufacturing",
      title: "Smart Factories: AI Transformation in Medical Scrub Production",
      date: "December 15, 2025",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A6c9a8add0496444fba0d8ebd8fc6c61cH.png",
      keywords: "AI garment manufacturing, smart factory, medical apparel trends",
      description: "How Yilong Scrubs integrated AI to solve the 'Slow Response' industry pain point.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">As we close out 2025, the medical apparel industry is no longer just about sewing; it's about data. At Yilong Scrubs, we've implemented an <strong>End-to-End AI Ecosystem</strong> in our Anhui facility to solve the industry's biggest nightmare: <em>The Lead Time Gap.</em></p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A6c9a8add0496444fba0d8ebd8fc6c61cH.png" alt="AI-driven design and pattern nesting" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl" />

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-8 italic text-slate-900">Solving the "Slow Response" Pain Point</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 italic">Waiting 14 days for a sample is a relic of the past. Our 2025 technology upgrade has introduced two revolutionary systems:</p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-8 mb-16">
          <li class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-2 italic">AI Pattern Nesting</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 italic">By using machine learning to calculate fabric cutting paths, we've reduced material waste by 12%. This efficiency translates directly into lower costs for our wholesale partners.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-2 italic">Predictive Supply Chain</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 italic">Our AI monitors global shipping trends and raw material costs, allowing us to pre-stock 72/21/7 fabric before price surges, ensuring 15-30 day bulk delivery even during peak seasons.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Precision Quality Control</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Inconsistent stitching is another major pain point. Our new computerized sewing stations now alert technicians in real-time if thread tension deviates by even 1%, guaranteeing that every Yilong scrub set meets our 20-year quality legacy.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "procurement-for-small-clinics",
      title: "Smart Procurement: Solving the High MOQ Barrier for Clinics",
      date: "June 20, 2025",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A204336e23ae14b80aa021d32eb19fa5fn.png",
      keywords: "clinic procurement, medical uniform wholesale, small clinic scrubs",
      description: "How to maintain a professional brand identity without the burden of excess inventory.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">For decades, small medical practices and startup scrub brands were ignored by large manufacturers. The "Pain Point" was clear: <strong>High Minimum Order Quantities (MOQs).</strong> Large factories often demanded 500+ sets per color, forcing clinics to either settle for generic, low-quality stock or tie up their entire budget in inventory.</p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A204336e23ae14b80aa021d32eb19fa5fn.png" alt="Custom branded scrub packaging for small orders" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl" />

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-8 italic text-slate-900">The 10-Set Revolution</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 italic">Yilong Scrubs has solved this by optimizing our production lines for small-batch efficiency. We've proven that quality doesn't have to mean massive volume.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border-l-8 border-primary my-16">
          <h4 class="font-black text-2xl mb-6 italic text-primary">Yilong's Agile Sourcing Model:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 italic font-medium">
            <li>✓ 10 Sets MOQ: Launch a new color with minimal risk.</li>
            <li>✓ 20 Sets Logo Customization: Build brand identity from day one.</li>
            <li>✓ 50 Sets Custom Packaging: Look like a premium global player immediately.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900 text-left">Ditching the "Generic" Look</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Many clinics settles for cheap 'one-size-fits-all' uniforms. Our agile model gives these clinics access to our high-performance 72/21/7 fabrics and tailored fits, allowing them to compete with large hospital groups in terms of professional image.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "hospital-color-trends-2024",
      title: "Hospital Color Trends 2024: Beyond the Basic Blue",
      date: "June 15, 2024",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A5def14b1fe684b58819971fb7f22d9b8y.png",
      keywords: "scrub colors, hospital uniform trends, medical fashion 2024",
      description: "Sage Green and Charcoal Grey: The psychology of color in modern healthcare.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">2024 has seen a psychological shift in medical spaces. Patients respond better to calming, sophisticated colors. The "Pain Point" of traditional hospitals was the 'clinical' cold blue feel, which often increased patient anxiety.</p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A5def14b1fe684b58819971fb7f22d9b8y.png" alt="Modern medical scrub color palette" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl" />

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-8 italic text-slate-900 underline decoration-primary decoration-4">The Psychology of the 2024 Palette</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-12 my-16 text-left">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-2xl mb-4 italic text-emerald-700">Sage Green & Hunter Green</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">Representing nature and renewal. These colors are now the #1 choice for pediatric and aesthetic clinics, creating a warm, approachable atmosphere.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-2xl mb-4 italic text-slate-700">Charcoal Grey & Graphite</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">The ultimate authoritative look. Preferred by specialized surgical units and hospital management for its sleek, modern aesthetic.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-black text-2xl mb-4 italic text-red-800">Burgundy / Wine</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">A sophisticated alternative to pink or red, projecting confidence and high-end professional care.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Solving the "Fading" Pain Point</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Nothing looks worse than a faded uniform. At Yilong, we use <strong>Reactive Dyeing Technology</strong>. Unlike standard pigments, reactive dyes form a chemical bond with the fiber, ensuring that these vibrant 2024 colors stay deep and rich even after 50+ industrial laundering cycles.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "sourcing-medical-apparel-guide",
      title: "Global Guide: Sourcing Medical Apparel from China",
      date: "December 12, 2021",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aec95977cfa6a4d1baef4aae1c2b42c5co.png",
      keywords: "source scrubs from China, medical garment factory, wholesale guide",
      description: "How to avoid the middleman trap and build a 20-year legacy brand.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">Sourcing from overseas can be a minefield of middlemen and generic quality. The "Pain Point" for international buyers is often the <strong>Lack of Transparency.</strong> Many traders pose as factories, leading to higher costs and zero quality control. Here is our 2021 guide to finding a true manufacturing partner.</p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aec95977cfa6a4d1baef4aae1c2b42c5co.png" alt="Organized fabric roll warehouse" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl" />

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-8 italic text-slate-900">The 5-Point Vetting Checklist</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-10 my-16 text-left">
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-primary">
            <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-3 italic">1. Verify Specialization</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 italic">If a factory makes t-shirts, jeans, and scrubs, they aren't a scrubs specialist. <strong>Yilong Scrubs is 100% focused.</strong> Our machinery is set specifically for the tension of Spandex-blend medical fabrics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-primary">
            <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-3 italic">2. Ask for the OEKO-TEX® ID</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 italic">Don't just take their word for it. Request the specific certificate ID and verify it on the OEKO-TEX website. This ensures the scrubs you sell won't cause skin reactions for healthcare workers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-primary">
            <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-3 italic">3. Direct-to-Floor Communication</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 italic">Can you speak to the person responsible for the sewing floor? If there are too many layers of "sales agents," your feedback will get lost in translation, leading to costly errors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Experience is the Best QC</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">A factory that has survived 20 years, like Yilong, has already faced every supply chain crisis imaginable. We have established raw material partnerships that newer factories simply cannot match, giving you stability in both price and quality.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "managing-supply-chain-crisis-2020",
      title: "Resilience: Managing the Supply Chain Crisis of 2020",
      date: "June 15, 2020",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A23446d76a9154c50bbffb0ad42bac9a7a.png",
      keywords: "supply chain resilience, manufacturing crisis, medical apparel delivery",
      description: "Lessons learned during the most challenging year in modern manufacturing history.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed italic text-slate-600">2020 redefined what it means to be a manufacturer. The world stopped, but the demand for medical apparel skyrocketed. The industry's pain point was clear: <strong>Total Supply Chain Collapse.</strong></p>
        
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A23446d76a9154c50bbffb0ad42bac9a7a.png" alt="Cinematic shipping port representing global logistics" class="rounded-[3rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover my-16 shadow-2xl" />

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-8 italic text-slate-900">How Yilong Stayed Operational</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 italic text-left">While many factories closed, Yilong Scrubs leaned on its 15-year (at the time) history of vertical integration. We don't just sew; we manage the fiber.</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 my-16 text-left italic">
          <div class="p-8 bg-blue-900 text-white rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl">
            <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-4 text-secondary">Local Sourcing Hub</h4>
            <p class="opacity-90">By keeping our raw material supply within Anhui, we avoided the cross-province lockdowns that paralyzed other manufacturers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl">
            <h4 class="font-black text-xl mb-4 text-white">Vertical Transparency</h4>
            <p class="opacity-90">We gave our global clients 24/7 access to our production logs via WhatsApp, providing peace of mind when they needed it most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Moving Forward: The Pro-Active Era</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 italic">The lessons of 2020 led us to invest in the smart inventory systems we use today. We no longer just react to orders; we anticipate global healthcare needs, ensuring our partners are never left without their essential professional gear.</p>
      `
    }
  ];

  return posts.map((post) => ({
    params: { slug: post.slug },
    props: { post },
  }));
}

const { post } = Astro.props;
---

<Layout 
  title={`${post.title} | Yilong Scrubs Blog`} 
  description={post.description}
  keywords={post.keywords}
>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-5xl">
    <a href="/blog" class="text-primary font-bold uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-widest hover:underline mb-8 md:mb-12 inline-block italic flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="text-lg">←</span> Back to Industry Insights
    </a>
    
    <header class="mb-12 md:mb-20 text-left border-b-2 border-slate-100 pb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="h-px w-12 bg-secondary"></span>
        <p class="text-sm font-black text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] italic">{post.date}</p>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-black italic text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-8 tracking-tighter">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-400 italic max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">{post.description}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-xl prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-700 leading-[1.8] italic font-medium selection:bg-secondary selection:text-white" set:html={post.content}>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-32 pt-16 border-t border-slate-100">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-10 md:p-20 rounded-[4rem] text-center shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 p-8 opacity-5">
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-96 h-96" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
           </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 italic text-white leading-tight">Solve Your Sourcing<br/>Pain Points Today</h3>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 italic text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Yilong Scrubs: 20 Years of Craftsmanship. 10-set MOQs. OEKO-TEX Safety. 72/21/7 Performance. Let's scale your brand together.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white font-black py-6 px-16 rounded-full text-xl uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-blue-800 transition shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">Work with Yilong Team</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/8615556105350" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-white text-slate-900 font-black py-6 px-16 rounded-full text-xl uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-50 transition shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">WhatsApp Marvin</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>